queries.text: SELECT id, note, last_updated FROM diary ORDER BY last_updated DESC
queries.name: ListDiaries

queries.text: SELECT id, note, last_updated FROM diary WHERE id = $1
queries.name: DiaryByID

queries.text:
INSERT INTO diary (id, note) VALUES ($1, $2)
RETURNING id, note, last_updated
queries.name: CreateDiary

queries.text:
UPDATE diary SET note = $2, last_updated = NOW() WHERE id = $1
RETURNING id, note, last_updated
queries.name: UpdateDiary
